### ------------------------------------------------------------------------
### HISTORIAL (DAILY RECORDS)
### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Crear un registro diario COMPLETO (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/history/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "date": "2023-10-30",
  "steps": 10500,
  "distance_km": 8.2,
  "calories_kcal": 550.0,
  "sleep_hours": 7.0,
  "sleep_quality": "Buena",
  "mood": 5,
  "hydration_ml": 2500,
  "activities": [
    {
      "activity_type": "Correr",
      "duration_minutes": 45
    },
    {
      "activity_type": "Caminata",
      "duration_minutes": 20
    }
  ]
}

### Obtener historial completo (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Actualizar un registro existente (PUT) - Reemplaza actividades
# NOTA: Reemplaza '1' con el ID real del registro que quieras editar
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/history/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "date": "2023-10-30",
  "steps": 12000,
  "distance_km": 9.5,
  "calories_kcal": 600.0,
  "sleep_hours": 7.5,
  "sleep_quality": "Excelente",
  "mood": 5,
  "hydration_ml": 3000,
  "activities": [
    {
      "activity_type": "Gimnasio",
      "duration_minutes": 60
    }
  ]
}

### Obtener detalle de un registro específico (GET)
# NOTA: Reemplaza '1' con el ID real
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}